Template to produce single or multiple [[non-breaking space]]s ("<code><big>&amp;nbsp;</big></code>"s). Uses {{tl|loop15}}.

; Syntax : <code><big><nowiki>{{spaces|</nowiki>''N''}}</big></code><br />where the optional parameter ''N'' is the desired number of consecutive non-breaking spaces (numeric, with a range of 1 to 15).

:<code><big><nowiki>{{spaces}}</nowiki></big></code><br />produces a single non-breaking space. You may also use {{tl|nbsp}} (which redirects to this template) as a shortcut for a single non-breaking space.

